</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="22.[151,1436,152,578]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,275,511,537]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Notes.</emphasis>
Externally resembling 
<taxonomicName authority="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta, 2010" authorityName="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta" authorityYear="2010" box="[548,772,512,537]" class="Insecta" family="Scirtidae" genus="Scirtes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="schawalleri" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[548,772,512,537]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Scirtes schawalleri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[778,843,512,538]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, from which it differs in slightly smaller body, apical macula with rounded anterolateral angle (acute in 
<taxonomicName authority="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta, 2010" authorityName="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta" authorityYear="2010" box="[780,917,552,577]" class="Insecta" family="Scirtidae" genus="Scirtes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="schawalleri" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[780,917,552,577]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">schawalleri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[924,988,552,578]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
), parameres not curved dorsally.
</paragraph>
